{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "The code already handles names when `adv_hex` is present in the URC — but the actual FC41DAAR03A09 firmware sends URCs without adv_data (`+QBLESCAN:,1,1f953971eae5`). Enabling **active scanning** (`AT+QBLESCANPARAM=1,...`) causes the module to send scan requests, triggering scan responses which contain device names. I'll add that one command before the scan start.", "ts": "2026-05-16T20:38:04+00:00", "time": "23:38:04"}
