{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "`AT+QBLESCANPARAM` is unsupported on this firmware and there are no BLE advertisers in range right now. Let me check the AT commands PDF to see what scan-mode options this firmware actually supports.", "ts": "2026-05-16T20:39:48+00:00", "time": "23:39:48"}
