{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "The manual reveals the truth: `AT+QBLESCAN=1` URC format is `+QBLESCAN:<name>,<addr_type>,<addr>` — the first field is the **device name**, not RSSI. The current parser mislabels it as `rssi_s`. The parser fix will make names appear immediately. Also: `AT+QBLESCAN=2,<timeout_ms>` (max 10000) adds adv_data for full name extraction.", "ts": "2026-05-16T20:40:57+00:00", "time": "23:40:57"}
